We can then modify the the image by changing the transform in the
existing transform node.

First we can try a simple translation:
\begin{verbatim}
(8) -> offsetx := 200::DF
   (8)  200.0
                                                      Type : DoubleFloat

(9) -> offsety := 200::DF
   (9)  200.0
